snippet.title: Gravity Well (GWELL) [PC Game] playthrough (Unlicensed)
snippet.description: A old space shooter PC Game. "Gravity Well". The whole subjective of this Game is to take over multiple Planets and fight Enemies by an encounter from a different Leaders or by these Planets themselfs. Due to Shareware Version of this Game it means if we defeat at least all of these Colonies and Frighters from an Enemy, the Game ends and you can't save and reload a existing Game.
